[I] Interpreter and compiler to be compatible with ARITY/PROLOG

[T] N-Prolog(NPL) is an interpreter and compiler to be superset of
[T] ARITY/PROLOG(MS-DOS). N-Prolog is NOT ISO-Prolog. Compatible with
[T] ARITY/PROLOG(MS-DOS).

